                javax.swing.ImageIcon icon,
                int price,
                int nutrition,
                int tastiness,
                int weight)
        Initialises all variables used by a FoodType instance.
        Parameters:
        name - The name of the food
        icon - The icon for this food
        price - How much it will cost to buy this food from the ingame store using ingame currency
        nutrition - How nutritious the food is - a more nutritious food will remove more hunger when consumed
        tastiness - How tasty the food is - a tastier food will increase happiness more when consumed
        weight - How heavy the food is
